msgid "The client's problem is about further education"
msgstr "Addysg pellach yw problem y cleient"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1807
msgid ""
"The problem is about a school, college or local authority's failure to\n"
"provide for a child or young person's educational needs, or specifically about the failure to provide the support set out in the assessment of their needs"
msgstr ""
"Mae'r broblem ynghylch methiant ysgol, coleg neu awdurdod lleol i\n"
"ddarparu ar gyfer anghenion addysgol plentyn neu unigolyn ifanc, neu'n benodol am y methiant i ddarparu'r gefnogaeth a nodir yn yr asesiad o'u hanghenion."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1814
msgid "The client's problem is about higher education"
msgstr "Addysg pellach yw problem y cleient"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1825
msgid "The client's problem is about transport"
msgstr "Trafnidiaeth yw problem y cleient"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1861
msgid "Any other issue"
msgstr "Unrhyw fater arall"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1867
msgid "The client is enquiring about an application or admissions appeal in the normal admissions round (ie reception and secondary school transfers)"
msgstr "Mae'r cleient yn holi ynghylch cais neu apêl addefiadau yn y rownd addefiadau arferol (h.y. trosglwyddiadau derbyn ac ysgol uwchradd)"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1892
msgid "Negligence in the provision of education"
msgstr "Esgeuluster mewn perthynas â darpariaeth addysg"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1908
msgid "The client's problem relates to special needs not being met properly for a child of compulsory school age, or a young person in compulsory or further education"
msgstr "Mae problem y cleient yn ymwneud ag anghenion arbennig sydd ddim yn cael eu bodloni'n iawn i blentyn mewn oedran ysgol gorfodol, neu unigolyn ifanc mewn addysg orfodol neu uwch"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1939
msgid "There has been a formal fixed term exclusion from school (a suspension) of up to five days and the child has not received more than one other fixed term exclusion in the last school year"
msgstr "Cafwyd gwaharddiad cyfnod penodol ffurfiol o'r ysgol (gwaharddiad dros dro) hyd at bum niwrnod, ac nid yw'r plentyn wedi cael mwy nac un gwaharddiad cyfnod penodol arall yn y flwyddyn ysgol ddiwethaf"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:1987
msgid "The client's problem is about SEN, transport, admissions or exclusions"
msgstr "Mae problem y cleient ynghylch SEN, trafnidiaeth, addefiadau neu waharddiadau"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2003
msgid "The client's problem is about fees or funding"
msgstr "Mae problem y cleient yn ymwneud â ffioedd neu gyllid "

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2035
msgid "The client's problem is about exclusion - but not for failure at exams or malpractice allegations eg plagiarism"
msgstr "Mae problem y cleient yn ymwneud â gwaharddiad - nid am fethu yn yr arholiadau neu honiadau camymddwyn e.e. llên-ladrad"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2069
msgid ""
"This refers to:\n"
"* pregnancy\n"
"* having recently given birth (and can include the need to breastfeed)"
msgstr ""
"Mae hyn yn cyfeirio at y canlynol:\n"
"* beichiogrwydd\n"
"* wedi rhoi genedigaeth yn ddiweddar (a gall gynnwys yr angen i fwydo ar y fron)"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2080
msgid "Race refers to a group of people defined by their race, colour, nationality (including citizenship), ethnic or national origins."
msgstr "Mae hil yn cyfeirio at grŵp o bobl sy'n cael eu diffinio gan eu hil, lliw, cenedligrwydd (gan gynnwys dinasyddiaeth), tarddiad ethnig neu wlad."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2086
msgid "Religion or belief (or lack of belief)"
msgstr "Crefydd neu gred (neu ddiffyg cred)"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2089
msgid ""
"Religion refers to any religious or philosophical belief. This also includes a lack of religious belief (eg atheism).\n"
"Generally, a belief should affect your life choices or the way you live for it to be included in the definition."
msgstr ""
"Mae crefydd yn cyfeirio at unrhyw gred grefyddol neu athronyddol. Mae hyn hefyd yn cynnwys diffyg cred grefyddol (e.e. anffyddiaeth).\n"
"Yn gyffredinol, dylai cred effeithio ar eich dewisiadau mewn bywyd, neu'r ffordd yr ydych yn byw iddo gael ei gynnwys yn y diffiniad. "

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2096
msgid "Sex"
msgstr "Rhyw"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2104
msgid "Sexual orientation"
msgstr "Cyfeiriadedd Rhywiol"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2107
msgid ""
"Sexual orientation is whether a person's sexual attraction is towards their own sex, the opposite sex or to both sexes.\n"
"This can also cover situations where discrimination is based on perceived sexual orientation, which may not be the case."
msgstr ""
"Cyfeiriadedd rhywiol yw pan mae atyniad rhywiol unigolyn tuag at ei ryw ei hun, y rhyw arall neu'r ddau ryw.\n"
"Gall hyn ymdrin â sefyllfaoedd lle mae gwahaniaethu wedi'i seilio ar gyfeiriadedd rhywiol ymddangosiadol, ond efallai nid fel yna mae hi."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2114
msgid "Gender reassignment"
msgstr "Ailbennu rhywedd"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2117
msgid ""
"It is unlawful to discriminate against someone due to their gender reassignment.\n"
"\n"
"This includes where someone is:\n"
"* is proposing to undergo gender reassignment\n"
"* is currently undergoing gender reassignment\n"
"* has already undergone (or partially undergone) the process of gender reassignment"
msgstr ""
"Mae'n anghyfreithlon i wahaniaethu yn erbyn rhywun oherwydd ailbennu rhywedd.\n"
"\n"
"Mae hyn yn cynnwys pan fydd rhywun:\n"
"* yn bwriadu cael triniaeth ailbennu rhywedd\n"
"* yn cael triniaeth ailbennu rhywedd ar hyn o bryd\n"
"* wedi bod drwy (neu wedi mynd drwy'n rhannol) y broses ailbennu rhywedd yn barod"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2136
msgid "Disability or failure to make reasonable adjustments for a disabled person"
msgstr "Anabledd neu fethiant i wneud addasiadau rhesymol ar gyfer unigolyn anabl"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2176
msgid "The client has been identified as homeless through a Community Care Assessment"
msgstr "Mae'r cleient wedi cael ei ddynodi'n ddigartref drwy Asesiad Gofal Cymunedol "

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2182
msgid "The client has not been identified as homeless through a Community Care Assessment"
msgstr "Nid yw'r cleient wedi cael ei ddynodi'n ddigartref drwy Asesiad Gofal Cymunedol"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2188
msgid "Client wants advice about international family maintenance"
msgstr "Mae'r cleient eisiau cyngor am gynhaliaeth teuluol rhyngwladol"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2191
msgid ""
"Covers enforcement of maintenance orders made outside the UK. Clients who have obtained maintenance orders in one country can apply to have them registered and enforced in another country. \n"
"\n"
"So where a client wants to obtain an order outside the UK this will not be in scope.\n"
"\n"
"**NOTE: These are very unusual cases.**"
msgstr ""
"Mae'n ymdrin â gorchmynion gorfodi cynhaliaeth a wneir y tu allan i'r DU. Gall cleientiaid sydd wedi cael gorchmynion cynhaliaeth mewn un wlad wneud cais i'w cofrestru a'u gorfodi mewn gwlad arall.\n"
"\n"
"Felly pan fydd cleient yn cael gorchymyn y tu allan i'r DU, ni fydd hyn o fewn cwmpas.\n"
"\n"
"** NODYN: Mae'r rhain yn achosion anghyffredin iawn."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2249
msgid "Not a Civil Legal Advice category or legal problem."
msgstr "Nid yw'n gategori Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil nac yn broblem gyfreithiol"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2263
msgid ""
"IMPORTANT: Where a client or a child is AT IMMEDIATE RISK OF ABUSE you must follow the Civil Legal Advice Child, Young Person and Adult at Risk of Abuse Policy. You may need to report the matter to protection services.\n"
"\n"
"*Click 'Next' to continue*"
msgstr ""
"PWYSIG: Lle bo cleient neu blentyn mewn PERYGL UNIONGYRCHOL O GAMDRINIAETH, mae'n rhaid i chi ddilyn y Polisi Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil ar gyfer Plentyn, Unigolyn Ifanc ac Oedolyn sydd mewn Perygl o Gamdriniaeth. Efallai bydd angen i chi adrodd y mater i'r gwasanaethau diogelu.\n"
"\n"
"* Cliciwch 'Nesaf' i barhau* "

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2271
msgid "Legal advice in support of family mediation"
msgstr "Cyngor cyfreithiol i gefnogi cyfryngu teuluol"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2274
msgid ""
"Family mediation can help people whose relationships have broken down to reach their own agreement about money, property and childcare, without going to court.\n"
"\n"
"If the client wants legal advice to support of ongoing or recently completed mediation process this will be in scope. This can include making any agreement reached in mediation legally binding by applying to the court (a consent order).\n"
"\n"
"*Please note: Mediation must be ongoing or have concluded. Clients will not qualify for Civil Legal Advice advice where mediation has not yet taken place or they have only attended Mediation Assessment Information Meeting (MIAM).*"
msgstr ""
"Gall cyfryngu teuluol helpu pobl sydd â pherthynas sydd wedi chwalu, i ddod i gytundeb eu hunain ynghylch arian, eiddo a gofal plant heb fynd i'r llys.\n"
"\n"
"Os yw'r cleient eisiau cyngor cyfreithiol i gefnogi proses cyfryngu parhaus neu gyfryngu sydd wedi dod i ben yn ddiweddar, yna bydd hyn o fewn y cwmpas. Gall hyn gynnwys gwneud unrhyw gytundeb a ddaethpwyd iddo yn y cyfarfod cyfryngu a'i rwymo mewn cyfraith drwy wneud cais i'r llys (gorchymyn cydsynio).\n"
"\n"
"* Sylwch: Rhaid i'r cyfryngu fod yn barhaus neu wedi dod i ben. Ni fydd cleientiaid yn gymwys am gyngor gan Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil os na fydd y cyfryngu wedi digwydd eto neu os mai dim ond Cyfarfod Cyfryngu, Gwybodaeth ac Asesu (MIAM) y maent wedi'i fynychu.*"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2292
msgid ""
"Please read out the following to the client:\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"*Based on what you have told me today your problem may be covered by legal aid. But you will still need to show that you qualify financially.*\n"
"\n"
"*I’m afraid that Civil Legal Advice does not provide advice about the issue that you are calling about. But our service is not your only option and I will direct you to alternative help.*\n"
"\n"
"*I can’t guarantee that these organisations/this organisation will take on your case under legal aid so please check with them to see whether they are able to help you. If you do not qualify for legal aid you may have to pay for their service. So check any costs, their opening hours and whether you can make an appointment. Also check any insurance policies you may have that provide legal cover as any potential costs may be covered by this.*"
msgstr ""
"Darllenwch y canlynol ar lafar i'r cleient:\n"
"\n"
"* Ar sail yr hyn yr ydych wedi ei ddweud wrthyf fi heddiw, efallai y byddwch yn gymwys i gael cymorth cyfreithiol am eich problem. Ond bydd rhaid i chi dal ddangos eich bod yn gymwys yn ariannol. * \n"
"\n"
"* Mae arna'i ofn nad yw Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil yn darparu cyngor ynghylch y mater yr ydych yn ffonio amdano i'w drafod. Ond nid ein gwasanaeth ni yw eich unig opsiwn, a byddaf yn ceisio eich cyfeirio at gymorth gwahanol.*\n"
"\n"
"* Ni allaf warantu y bydd y sefydliadau/ sefydliad hwn yn cymryd eich achos dan gymorth cyfriethiol, felly gwiriwch gyda hwy i weld os allant eich helpu. Os nad ydych yn gymwys am gymorth cyfreithiol efallai bydd rhaid i chi dalu am eu gwasanaeth. Felly gwiriwch unrhyw gostau, eu horiau agor ac os gallwch wneud apwyntiad. Hefyd, gwiriwch unrhyw bolisiau yswiriant sydd gennych a allai ddarparu sicrwydd cyfreithiol oherwydd efallai y bydd yn talu am unrhyw gostau posibl.*"

