#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2706
msgid "Domestic abuse (including psychological, physical, financial, sexual or emotional abuse, forced marriage, child abduction, female genital mutilation and harassment). Also includes defence against a non-molestation or occupation order where the client is the alleged abuser."
msgstr "Cam-drin domestig (gan gynnwys cam-drin seicolegol, corfforol, ariannol, rhywiol neu emosiynol, priodas dan orfod, herwgydio plentyn, anffurfio organau cenhedlu menywod ac aflonyddu). Hefyd yn cynnwys amddiffyn yn erbyn gorchymyn anheddu neu orchymyn rhag molestu os mai'r cleient yw'r camdriniwr honedig."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2709
msgid ""
"Where a Client wants to seek a court order to protect themselves or a child from abuse via a court order 'an injunction' that tells a person they're not allowed to do a certain act.\n"
"\n"
"Some clients who are the alleged abuser do not agree with the injunction against them and wish to get help in defending themselves against it.\n"
"\n"
"Guidance contains an article \"Domestic violence and abuse - definition\" for more information. Search for 'dv' or 'abuse' to find it quickest."
msgstr ""
"Pan fo cleient eisiau ceisio am orchymyn llys i ddiogelu eu hunain neu blentyn rhag cam-drin drwy orchymyn llys 'gwaharddeb' sy'n dweud wrth unigolyn nad ydynt yn cael cyflawni gweithred benodol. \n"
"\n"
"Ni fydd rhai cleientiaid sy'n gamdrinwyr honedig yn cytuno â'r waharddeb yn eu herbyn ac yn dymuno cael cymorth i amddiffyn eu hunain yn ei erbyn.\n"
"\n"
"Mae'r Canllaw yn cynnwys erthygl \"Trais a Cham-drin Domestig - diffiniad\" i gael rhagor o wybodaeth. Chwiliwch am 'dv' neu 'abuse' i ddod o hyd iddi'n gynt."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2717
msgid "Forced marriage - the client wants advice"
msgstr "Priodas dan orfod - mae'r cleient eisiau cyngor"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2720
msgid "This is where a marriage is about to take place or has taken place without the full and free consent of each party. This may be due to actual or threats of physical force or violence, emotional pressure or psychological abuse. Civil Legal Advice Specialists can offer advice on seeking an order to protect the client from such a marriage occuring or how to end such a marriage."
msgstr "Dyma lle mae priodas ar fin cael ei chynnal neu wedi'i chynnal heb ganiatâd llawn a rhydd gan bob parti. Gall hyn fod oherwydd bygythiadau gwirioneddol neu fygythiadau i drais neu rym corfforol, pwysau emosiynol neu gam-drin seicolegol. Gall Arbenigwyr Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil gynnig cyngor ar geisio am orchymyn i ddiogelu'r cleient rhag i briodas o'r fath ddigwydd neu sut i ddod â phriodas o'r fath i ben. "

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2762
msgid ""
"Is there a dispute for which family mediation is relevant? If so, please check if client has heard of/and considered Family Mediation.\n"
"\n"
"*On the following screen please select if they want to find a local mediator, or that mediation isn't relevant to the problem. Click next to continue.*"
msgstr ""
"A oes anghydfod lle mae cyfryngu teuluol yn berthnasol? Os oes, gwiriwch os yw'r cleient wedi clywed am/ac wedi ystyried Cyfryngu Teuluol.\n"
"\n"
"* Ar y sgrîn ganlynol, bydd angen dewis os ydynt angen cyfryngwr lleol, neu os nad yw cyfryngu yn berthnasol i'r broblem. Cliciwch nesaf i barhau.*"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2767
msgid ""
"Family mediators are trained to work with people whose relationships have broken down. They will listen to both sides of the argument and help you to reach your own agreement about money, property and childcare, without going to court.\n"
"\n"
"It is not just separating couples that can use mediation. It may also help grandparents or step-families resolve their issues.\n"
"\n"
"Mediation provides a safe and neutral setting for you to talk and explore your concerns and needs to each other.\n"
"\n"
"Search for 'Family Mediation' in the guidance search box for more help.\n"
"\n"
"If you are qualify you can get legal aid for family mediation as well as legal advice to support the mediation process. This can include the cost of making any agreement that you reach in mediation legally binding by applying to the court - this is called applying for a consent order."
msgstr ""
"Mae cyfryngwyr teuluol wedi cael eu hyfforddi i weithio gyda phobl sydd â pherthynas wedi chwalu. Byddant yn gwrando ar ddwy ochr o'r ddadl ac yn eich helpu i ddod i gytundeb eich hunain ynghylch arian, eiddo a gofal plant, heb fynd i'r llys.\n"
"\n"
"Nid cyplau sy'n gwahanu yn unig y gall ddefnyddio gwasanaeth cyfryngu. Gall helpu teidiau a neiniau neu lys deuluoedd i ddatrys eu problemau.\n"
"\n"
"Mae cyfryngu yn darparu sefyllfa ddiogel a diduedd i chi siarad ac edrych ar eich pryderon ac anghenion eich gilydd.\n"
"\n"
"Chwiliwch am 'Cyfryngu Teuluol' yn y blwch chwilio yn y canllaw i gael rhagor o gymorth.\n"
"\n"
"Os ydych yn gymwys cewch gymorth cyfreithiol i gael cyfryngu teuluol yn ogystal â chyngor cyfreithiol i'ch cefnogi yn y broses cyfryngu. Gall hyn gynnwys cost o wneud unrhyw gytundeb yr ydych yn dod iddo yn y cyfryngu yn rhwymo mewn cyfraith drwy ei gyflwyno i'r llys - gelwir hyn yn gwneud cais am orchymyn cydsynio."

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2779
msgid "Client wishes to find mediator."
msgstr "Cleient yn dymuno dod o hyd i gyfryngwr"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2785
msgid "Client does not wish to find a mediator."
msgstr "Nid yw'r cleient yn dymuno dod o hyd i gyfryngwr"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2791
msgid ""
"Please read the following to the client:\n"
"\n"
"*If you have Internet access I can tell you where to find more information about Family Mediation and how to search for a family mediator.*\n"
"\n"
"*Or I can find a family mediation service for you now.*\n"
"\n"
"*If you qualify you may be able to get legal aid to cover the costs of Family Mediation as well as legal advice to support the mediation process. Or you may need to pay for the service. Please speak to the mediation service to find out more.*\n"
"\n"
"You should now direct the client to their nearest contracted quality assured family mediation service using the directory (Find An Adviser tool)"
msgstr ""
"Darllenwch y canlynol i'r cleient:\n"
"\n"
"* Os oes gennych fynediad i'r rhyngrwyd, gallaf ddweud wrthych ble i gael rhagor o wybodaeth am Gyfryngu Teuluol a sut i chwilio am gyfryngwr teuluol.*\n"
"\n"
"* Neu gallaf ddod o hyd i wasanaeth cyfryngu teuluol i chi yn awr.*\n"
"\n"
"* Os ydych yn gymwys efallai y cewch gymorth cyfreithiol i dalu costau Cyfryngu Teuluol yn ogystal â chyngor cyfreithiol i gefnogi'r broses gyfryngu. Neu efallai bydd angen i chi dalu am y gwasanaeth hwn. Siaradwch â'r gwasanaeth cyfryngu i gael rhagor o wybodaeth.*\n"
"\n"
"Dylech gyfeirio'r cleient i'r gwasanaeth cyfryngu teuluol agosaf sydd â sicrhad ansawdd gan ddefnyddio'r cyfeiriadur (arf Dod o hyd i Gynghorwr)"

#: apps/diagnosis/data/graph.graphml.tpl:2804
msgid "The client has already taken action to stop domestic abuse (e.g. via an injunction) but needs to take further action as the order is not being complied with"
msgstr "Mae'r cleient eisoes wedi cymryd camau i atal cam-drin domestig (e.e. drwy waharddeb) ond mae angen cymryd camau pellach gan na chydymffurfir â'r gorchymyn "

